{"tid":2271580,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Make America Great Again","createTime":"2020-11-04T15:29:40.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-14T05:00:43.000Z","uid":16055,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"4ecd914a3cc9cdf04e05bfc78fe70c9b01d22771","tid":2271580,"uid":16055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T15:29:40.000Z","msg":"呢一刻心情真係好沉重<br />\n明明係美國人選舉點解會咁關心<br />\n呢種係咪愛國 但我又唔係美國人<br />\n究竟咩係愛國 <br />\n呢次係最後的希望 係End Game 但結果...<br />\n窮人繼續含撚 有錢人繼續奶共<br />\n其實我地先係左膠 想美國打救世界<br />\n借他人之手實現世界和平實現大愛<br />\n世界本來就係黑暗 我唔知世界以後會點<br />\n根本沒有能克服絕望的辦法 我們只有繼續向前進而已<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"baa429757cc19d2afe6b3857818e992b5f6b987f","tid":2271580,"uid":16055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T16:02:32.000Z","msg":"侵侵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9f8240b6db59b32c53f64c0183a865bde49c154","tid":2271580,"uid":2377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T16:17:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f5774916662a53014e5d0e5509434017b6da682","tid":2271580,"uid":16055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T05:00:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}